        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks AA for letter on coral reefs. "I used to think … that areas of elevation and of subsidence must – as a general rule be separated by a single great line of fissure, or rather of several".</p>
            <p>Suggests that AA urge again his views on reappearance of old characters.</p>
        </abstract>
